<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Owner Dashboard - Fullstack Cafe</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-slate-100 min-h-screen font-sans text-slate-900">

    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto my-12 px-5">
        <header class="mb-10 text-center md:text-left">
            <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-slate-800">Owner Dashboard</h1>
            <p class="text-slate-500 mt-2 text-base">Welcome back, Admin. Here is your cafe's performance.</p>
        </header>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-12">
            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm flex flex-col border-l-[5px] border-yellow-400 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-yellow-400/20">
                <strong class="text-xs text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-widest font-semibold">Total Orders</strong>
                <span class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-800 mt-2"><%= stats.orders %></span>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm flex flex-col border-l-[5px] border-green-500 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-green-500/20">
                <strong class="text-xs text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-widest font-semibold">Total Revenue</strong>
                <span class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-800 mt-2"><%= stats.revenue %></span>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-sm flex flex-col border-l-[5px] border-yellow-400 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-yellow-400/20">
                <strong class="text-xs text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-widest font-semibold">Support Requests</strong>
                <span class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-800 mt-2"><%= stats.messages %></span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-xl hover:border-slate-200 group">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2 group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">Product Management</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-500 mb-6 text-sm">Add, edit, or remove items from your menu.</p>
                <a href="/admin/add-product" class="inline-block bg-slate-800 text-white px-5 py-2.5 rounded-lg font-semibold text-sm transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-yellow-400 hover:text-black hover:scale-105 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg">Manage Menu</a>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-xl hover:border-slate-200 group">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2 group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">Order Management</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-500 mb-6 text-sm">Update customer order statuses.</p>
                <a href="/admin/orders" class="inline-block bg-slate-800 text-white px-5 py-2.5 rounded-lg font-semibold text-sm transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-yellow-400 hover:text-black hover:scale-105 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg">Manage Orders</a>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-slate-100 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-xl hover:border-slate-200 group">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-2 group-hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors">Customer Messages</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-500 mb-6 text-sm">View latest support requests from users.</p>
                <a href="/admin/messages" class="inline-block bg-slate-800 text-white px-5 py-2.5 rounded-lg font-semibold text-sm transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-yellow-400 hover:text-black hover:scale-105 shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg">View Inbox</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>